    <title>Mybatis在XML中该如何取参数</title>
    <url>/2020/02/26/Mybatis%E5%9C%A8XML%E4%B8%AD%E8%AF%A5%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%8F%96%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="Mybatis在XML中该如何取参数"><a href="#Mybatis在XML中该如何取参数" class="headerlink" title="Mybatis在XML中该如何取参数"></a>Mybatis在XML中该如何取参数</h2><blockquote>
<p>以Mybatis 3.5.3为例</p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li>org.apache.ibatis.reflection.ParamNameResolver<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x2F;**</span><br><span class="line">   * &lt;p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">   * 处理方法参数</span><br><span class="line">   * &lt;&#x2F;p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">   *&#x2F;</span><br><span class="line">public ParamNameResolver(Configuration config, Method method) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &#x2F;&#x2F; 获取参数列表中每个参数的类型</span><br><span class="line">    final Class&lt;?&gt;[] paramTypes &#x3D; method.getParameterTypes();</span><br><span class="line">    &#x2F;&#x2F; 获取每个标了 @Param 注解的参数的值,赋值给 name</span><br><span class="line">    final Annotation[][] paramAnnotations &#x3D; method.getParameterAnnotations();</span><br><span class="line">    &#x2F;&#x2F; 记录参数索引与参数名称的关系</span><br><span class="line">    final SortedMap&lt;Integer, String&gt; map &#x3D; new TreeMap&lt;&gt;();</span><br><span class="line">    int paramCount &#x3D; paramAnnotations.length;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    &#x2F;&#x2F; 遍历方法参数</span><br><span class="line">    for (int paramIndex &#x3D; 0; paramIndex &lt; paramCount; paramIndex++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      &#x2F;&#x2F; 是否为特殊参数：RowBounds或ResultHandler,是则跳过</span><br><span class="line">      if (isSpecialParameter(paramTypes[paramIndex])) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        &#x2F;&#x2F; skip special parameters</span><br><span class="line">        continue;</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;</span><br><span class="line">      String name &#x3D; null;</span><br><span class="line">      for (Annotation annotation : paramAnnotations[paramIndex]) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        &#x2F;&#x2F; 标注了 @Param 注解：name的值为注解的值</span><br><span class="line">        if (annotation instanceof Param) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">          hasParamAnnotation &#x3D; true;</span><br><span class="line">          name &#x3D; ((Param) annotation).value();</span><br><span class="line">          break;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;</span><br><span class="line">      &#x2F;&#x2F; 没有标 @Param 注解</span><br><span class="line">      if (name &#x3D;&#x3D; null) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        &#x2F;&#x2F; 全局配置：useActualParamName,默认为true,使用方法参数名为name</span><br><span class="line">        if (config.isUseActualParamName()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">          name &#x3D; getActualParamName(method, paramIndex);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        if (name &#x3D;&#x3D; null) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">          &#x2F;&#x2F; name为map.size()：相当于当前元素的索引，0，1，2，3</span><br><span class="line">          name &#x3D; String.valueOf(map.size());</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;</span><br><span class="line">      map.put(paramIndex, name);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    names &#x3D; Collections.unmodifiableSortedMap(map);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  &#x2F;**</span><br><span class="line">   * &lt;p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">   * 获取参数</span><br><span class="line">   * &lt;&#x2F;p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">   *&#x2F;</span><br><span class="line">  public Object getNamedParams(Object[] args) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    final int paramCount &#x3D; names.size();</span><br><span class="line">    if (args &#x3D;&#x3D; null || paramCount &#x3D;&#x3D; 0) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      &#x2F;&#x2F;没有参数</span><br><span class="line">      return null;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; else if (!hasParamAnnotation &amp;&amp; paramCount &#x3D;&#x3D; 1) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      &#x2F;&#x2F; 未使用@Param注解且参数列表只有一个,即 args[0] 参数的值</span><br><span class="line">      return args[names.firstKey()];</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; else &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      &#x2F;&#x2F; 为参数创建 param+ 索引的格式作为默认参数名称 如：param1  下标从1开始</span><br><span class="line">      final Map&lt;String, Object&gt; param &#x3D; new ParamMap&lt;&gt;();</span><br><span class="line">      int i &#x3D; 0;</span><br><span class="line">      &#x2F;&#x2F; 遍历names集合 key:方法参数的下标,value:方法参数名</span><br><span class="line">      for (Map.Entry&lt;Integer, String&gt; entry : names.entrySet()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        &#x2F;&#x2F;将参数存入param中,key:参数名,value:参数值</span><br><span class="line">        param.put(entry.getValue(), args[entry.getKey()]);</span><br><span class="line">        &#x2F;&#x2F; add generic param names (param1, param2, ...)</span><br><span class="line">        final String genericParamName &#x3D; GENERIC_NAME_PREFIX + String.valueOf(i + 1);</span><br><span class="line">        &#x2F;&#x2F; ensure not to overwrite parameter named with @Param</span><br><span class="line">        if (!names.containsValue(genericParamName)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">          &#x2F;&#x2F;将参数额外存一份到param中,使用key为param1...paramN</span><br><span class="line">          param.put(genericParamName, args[entry.getKey()]);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        i++;</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;</span><br><span class="line">      return param;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


</li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
<p>所以Mybatis 3.5.3在xml中取参数应该用以下方式</p>
</blockquote>
<ol>
<li>参数名.属性</li>
<li>@Param(“user”)注解,#{user.name}</li>
<li>参数下标 paramN,从1开始,参数在第一位#{param1.name},参数在第二位则#{param2.name},以此类推</li>
</ol>
]]></content>
